      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        Helping Hands is a nonprofit organization made up of dedicated volunteer firefighters committed to protecting lives, homes, and natural environments from the threat of wildfires in South Africa.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Our mission is to reduce the impact of wildfires by offering rapid emergency response, engaging in wildfire prevention, and empowering communities through education and training.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>
        We envision a South Africa where every community is equipped to coexist with wildfire through proactive safety, resilience, and unity. We aim to be leaders in fire management and environmental stewardship.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Team</h2>
